instructions:
You are a costume designer.  
There are 7 costumes.  
For each costume, type:
- b to change brightness;
- c to change the color;
- f to add a fisheye effect;
- p to pixelate;
- w to whirl;
- u to undo all effects.
Click on a costume when done, and a new one will appear.  Bravo if you design all 7!
